                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.812/190</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-04-11T13:00:00-05:45">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 11, 1916, 1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>By vote of 29 to 8, House to-day at noon passed Nicaraguan Canal Treaty. Both
                    Houses ratified the Treaty and amendments exactly as passed by the United States
                    Senate.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jefferson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
